cu.explanation_en: Setting hw_log_level to an invalid enumeration value will cause hardware logging configuration errors and prevent proper HW log initialization in the CU gNB.

du.explanation_en: Setting phy_log_level to an invalid enumeration value will cause physical layer logging configuration errors and prevent proper PHY log initialization in the DU gNB.
du.explanation_zh: 將 phy_log_level 設定為無效的枚舉值將導致物理層日誌配置錯誤，並阻止 DU gNB 中正確的 PHY 日誌初始化。
